Inflict Warpwave	KEY:Inflict Warpwave ~ Imentesh	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DEFINE:ImenteshWarpwaveDC|0	DESC:As a standard action, an imentesh can inflict a warpwave upon any corporeal creature within 100 feet.  The target can resist the warpwave's effects with a DC %1 Fortitude save.  If the imentesh wishes, it can use this ability as a swift action, but if it does so, it is affected by the warpwave as well unless it resists the effects with its own Fortitude save.  See page 213 for a list of possible effects caused by a warpwave.|ImenteshWarpwaveDC	BONUS:VAR|ImenteshWarpwaveDC|10+TL/2+CON	BONUS:VAR|ImenteshWarpwaveDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Inflict Warpwave)	SOURCEPAGE:p.214
Change Shape	KEY:Change Shape ~ Imentesh		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural						DESC:You have the ability to assume the appearance of a type of creature, but retain most of your own physical qualities.																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.214	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(greater polymorph)	BENEFIT:You have the ability to assume the appearance of a specific type of creature, but retain most of your own physical qualities. You cannot change shape to a form more than one size category smaller or larger than your original form. This ability functions as a greater polymorph spell, but you do not adjust your ability scores (although you gain any other abilities of the creature you mimic).

