Natural Invisibility	KEY:Natural Invisibility ~ Quickling	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Defensive.Supernatural	DESC:A quickling is invisible when motionless.  It loses this invisibility and remains visible for 1 round in any round in which it takes an action other than a free action.																													SOURCEPAGE:p.227
Supernatural Speed	KEY:Supernatural Speed ~ Quickling		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Defensive.Supernatural	DESC:A quickling moves with incredible speed.  Save for when it remains motionless (at which point it is invisible), the quickling's shape blurs and shimmers with this speed, granting it concealment (20%% miss chance).  In addition, this ability grants the quickling evasion and uncanny dodge (as the rogue abilities of the same names).	SOURCEPAGE:p.227
