Fear Aura								KEY:Fear Aura ~ Quickwood					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aura.Supernatural			DEFINE:QuickwoodFearAuraDC|0	DESC:A quickwood with stored magical energy can activate its fear aura as a standard action.  The aura has a raius of 10 feet per spell level of the effect and lasts for 1 round (Will DC %1 negates).  Creatures that fail their saving throw become panicked for 1 minute.|QuickwoodFearAuraDC									BONUS:VAR|QuickwoodFearAuraDC|10+TL/2+CHA	BONUS:VAR|QuickwoodFearAuraDC|4|TYPE=Racial	BONUS:VAR|QuickwoodFearAuraDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Fear Aura)	SOURCEPAGE:p.228	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(variable distance, DC %1)|QuickwoodFearAuraDC
Oaksight								KEY:Oaksight ~ Quickwood					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Sense.Supernatural								DESC:A quickwood may observe the area surrounding any oak tree within 360 feet as if using clairaudience/clairvoyance.  It can use this ability on any number of oak trees in the area.  Although the quickwood does not need line of silght to establish this link, if it does have line of sight to even a single oak tree, it cannot be flanked.																												SOURCEPAGE:p.228
Roots									KEY:Roots ~ Quickwood						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary						DESC:A quickwood has dozens of long roots, but can only attack with up to six of them in any given round.  If the quickwood uses its pull ability to pull a target within reach of its bite attack, it can immediately make a free bite attack with a +4 bonus on its attack roll against that target.																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.228
